<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />开始了呀，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="8" />的烟花大会<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么会是怎样的一场表演呢，<delay20 />真令人期待。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也是来看烟花的吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在胸腔震荡的重低音，<delay20 />
听到这声响我都兴奋起来了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在我小的时候，<delay20 />祖母曾牵着我的手<delay20 />
带我去看过烟花，<delay20 />
那场烟花大会我怎么也忘不了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那时候遇到的<delay20 />
穿浴衣的漂亮姐姐，<delay20 />
不知她现在过得如何<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在夜空的幕布上绽放的大朵烟花，<delay20 />
盛放后决然飘零<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这短短一瞬中包含着美学。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />烟花也有许多不同的种类。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />无论颜色形状，每种烟花都有自己的特点，<delay20 />
让人一瞬都不愿挪开眼。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我说，<tag a="110" b="4" />。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也在电视剧之类中<delay20 />看到过这样的场景吧？<delay20 />
烟花的声响掩盖了告白的话语。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在试一试，你听好哦。<10_4 />
<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><size value="150" />我一直很喜欢你！<size value="100" /><pageBreak /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎么样？<delay8 />我的声音，<delay20 />
你有听清楚吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />烟花<delay20 />真美啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，你知道这世上其实还有<delay20 />
更美的东西吗，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />？<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就是看着烟花绽放笑颜的<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你的脸庞……<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每当这种时候，<delay20 />
我都会将美景<delay20 />
印刻在心中的照相机里。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其中有一种<delay20 />
不存在于照片或录像里的<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />独特趣味。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />马上就要到时间了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />每次<delay20 />烟花升空的时候，<delay20 />
我都会在心里许愿。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />“希望这座<tag a="110" b="32" />永远和平。”<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />“希望可以和你永远亲密无间。”<10_4 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这些愿望都会实现的，我现在这么感觉。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然越是愉快的经历越希望它能永恒，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但正是因为时间有限，<delay20 />
才能制造出特别的回忆。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你在烟花大会上玩得开心吗，<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在的心情<delay20 />也格外好！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>